## What is Aviasales?

Aviasales is a metasearch engine for flights that searches and compares prices from over 800 airlines and travel agencies. Founded in 2007, it has grown to become one of the most trusted flight search platforms globally, with a presence in over 40 languages and more than 200 countries.

Whether you're planning a weekend getaway, a business trip, or a round-the-world adventure, Aviasales makes it easy to find the best deals available — all in one place.

## Why Travelers Choose Aviasales

### 1. Compare Prices from Over 800 Airlines

Aviasales searches across a vast network of airlines and travel agencies to bring you the most comprehensive list of flight options. From major carriers like Emirates and British Airways to budget airlines like Ryanair and easyJet, you'll find every option in one search.

### 2. Price Calendar and Alerts

Flight prices fluctuate constantly. Aviasales' price calendar shows you the cheapest days to fly, helping you plan your trip around the best deals. You can also set up price alerts to get notified when fares drop for your preferred route — so you never miss a bargain.

### 3. Search by Month or Entire Year

Unlike most booking sites that lock you into specific dates, Aviasales allows you to search for the cheapest flights across a whole month or even an entire year. This flexibility makes it perfect for travelers with flexible schedules who want to maximize their savings.

### 4. Direct Booking with Trusted Partners

Aviasales connects you directly to trusted airlines and travel agencies. When you find a flight you like, you're redirected to book directly with the provider. There are no hidden fees or middleman markups — you get the price you see.

### 5. User Reviews and Ratings

Aviasales includes reviews and ratings from real travelers for each flight option. This helps you make an informed decision, balancing price with airline reliability and service quality.

### 6. Mobile App for Convenience

The Aviasales mobile app lets you search, compare, and book flights on the go. Available for both iOS and Android, it's designed for travelers who want to plan their trips anytime, anywhere.

